## Brand positioning statement

> **Bonneval Fine Wines** is Sofia's sole gateway to ten of Burgundy's most revered domaines. Born from French roots and built on direct relationships with the vignerons themselves, Bonneval offers its private members privileged access to wines that never reach the open market — allocated by trust, delivered with the quiet authority of a century-old négociant, and presented with the precision of a maison de luxe. We do not sell wine. We extend invitations.

